<h2 id="optimal-workshop">Optimal Workshop</h2>

<p><a href="https://www.optimalworkshop.com/">Optimal Workshop</a> offers a suite of tools which can be used to test your product. These include:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.optimalworkshop.com/101/tree-testing">Tree testing</a> to test your Information Architecture</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.optimalworkshop.com/101/first-click-testing">Card sorting</a> to devise your Information Architecture</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.optimalworkshop.com/101/first-click-testing">First click testing</a> to test your User Interface</li>
</ul>
